Buy and Keep launched in April 2014 for Sky+HD subscribers . 
  It lets people stream movies straight to their TV, or to their mobiles using an app . 
  Films can also be watched across multiple devices using a 'follow me' function . 
  Sky launched the scheme for customers this time last year but it is now available to everyone in the UK and Ireland . 
